========== KingsRSS ==========

KingsRSS is a self-hosted tool to aggregate and send RSS feeds to your Kindle.

Deployment:

pip install -r requirements.txt

Configuration:

Edit srcconf.yml to add your RSS feeds and set email options.

For advanced users, you can edit kingsrss.py to customize the aggregating 
process. See comments for detailed explanation.

Usage:

For one-time tests, run:

python kingsrss.py

If you want to run KingsRSS regularly, you can create a cron job. Google for 
instructions on how to do this for your operating system.
